de.fhg.fit.biomos.sensorplatform.sensor

Interface SensorCommands

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractHeartRateSensor, AbstractPulseOximeterSensor, AbstractSensor, AdidasHRM, BLE113, CC2650, PolarH7, TomTomHRM

    public interface SensorCommands
    Defines methods, which are called from the corresponding SensorWrapper. Currently only two commands are supported, enable and disable notifications. Other commands can be added in the future (for example reading battery status).
    Author:
    Daniel Pyka
